  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Let's have peaceful protests'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Inspector General of Police CT Wickramaratne said that people have the right to hold peaceful protests.",
        "He said this while participating in the press conference held yesterday (07).",
        "People's representatives, politicians and religious leaders should act responsibly.",
        "Also, actions should be taken in such a way that there is no damage to private and government properties.",
        "At the same time, Inspector General of Police C. D. Wickramaratne has requested that government and private sector employees who are engaged in official duties should not be disturbed and enjoy their basic rights within the law. (a)"
      ],
